snippet.title: Official Gameplay Trailer 2025 l Castle of Blackwater
snippet.description:
🎮 Official 2025 Gameplay Trailer for Castle of Blackwater🎮  

The wait is almost over! Get an exclusive look at the gameplay for Castle of Blackwater and prepare for our demo launch during Steam Next Fest in February 2025. Play with your friends, enjoy the action, and share your thoughts with our community on Discord!  

🔗 Wishlist us on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2265920/Castle_of_Blackwater/ 
💬 Join our Discord Community: https://discord.gg/castle-of-blackwater  
📜 Read the Backstory: https://medium.com/@Blackwater_Town
📢 Follow us for updates: https://x.com/Blackwater_Town

🎵 Music by @RomanSenykMusic: https://youtu.be/sl9t-bWRESs?si=nSHGs7fXuDCWGmaV
